      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 64: `showOriginal` is delegate-local state but is not reset when `Body`, `OriginalBody`, or the represented message changes. In a recycled ListView delegate, a user can toggle one message to original and then see another message rendered in original mode unexpectedly. Reset the toggle when the message identity or overwrite state changes.\n```suggestion\n    onIdChanged: showOriginal \u003d false\n    onIsPluginOverwriteChanged: if (!isPluginOverwrite) showOriginal \u003d false\n```",
      "revId": "636a836e17213e544ba8574fc0073e7b2b4cee92",
      "serverId": "1e26b4c1-6b8c-47ff-9df7-501b633d3b5a"
    },
