      "writtenOn": "2026-05-20T20:14:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 65: `isPluginOverwrite: Body !\u003d\u003d OriginalBody` will classify messages as modified whenever `OriginalBody` is unset, empty, or absent for older/non-plugin messages. That risks showing a false \"Modified by extension\" indicator for normal messages. Gate the comparison on `OriginalBody` actually being present.\n```suggestion\n    property bool isPluginOverwrite: OriginalBody !\u003d\u003d \"\" \u0026\u0026 Body !\u003d\u003d OriginalBody\n```",
      "revId": "636a836e17213e544ba8574fc0073e7b2b4cee92",
      "serverId": "1e26b4c1-6b8c-47ff-9df7-501b633d3b5a"
    },
