      "writtenOn": "2026-05-20T20:14:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 80: When `showOriginal` is true, the delegate returns `OriginalBody` directly and bypasses the existing `MessagesAdapter.parseMessage(...)` path. That means the original text will not get the same parsing/sanitization/link-preview handling as the displayed body, which can cause inconsistent rendering and may expose raw markup depending on the Text component format. Use the same parsing pipeline for the selected body instead of returning `OriginalBody` directly.\n```suggestion\n                var displayBody \u003d showOriginal \u0026\u0026 isPluginOverwrite ? OriginalBody : Body;\n                if (displayBody !\u003d\u003d \"\" \u0026\u0026 ParsedBody.length \u003d\u003d\u003d 0) {\n                    MessagesAdapter.parseMessage(Id, displayBody, UtilsAdapter.getAppValue(Settings.DisplayHyperlinkPreviews), rootDelegate.colorUrl, bubble.color);\n                    return \"\";\n                }\n```",
      "revId": "636a836e17213e544ba8574fc0073e7b2b4cee92",
      "serverId": "1e26b4c1-6b8c-47ff-9df7-501b633d3b5a"
    },
    {
      "unresolved": true,
      "key": {
        "uuid": "3bf81463_fd643de3",
