      "writtenOn": "2026-05-20T20:14:43Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "[Critical] Line 81: The fallback `PreviousBodies[0].body` can dereference an empty or undefined history if `showOriginal` remains true while the delegate is reused for a non-plugin-overwritten message. QML ListView delegates can be recycled, so state stored on the delegate should be reset or guarded. Since the toggle is only shown for plugin overwrites, avoid reading edit history here or guard it explicitly.\n```suggestion\n                if (showOriginal \u0026\u0026 isPluginOverwrite)\n                    return OriginalBody;\n```",
      "revId": "636a836e17213e544ba8574fc0073e7b2b4cee92",
